snippet.textDisplay: I love the song however, please be inclusive to other artists as well instead of having Ali Zafar and Momina Mustehsan or any other singer sing multiple songs in a single season. We also need more Balochi and Kashmiri songs. I absolutely love Shabnam Majeed's voice she definitely deserves to be in coke studio and I am missing the rustic feel of saaen Zahoor's singing. Lastly, please give Rachel viccaji the opportunity to sing solo in the next season I am just mesmerized by the range of her vocals and It about time we get to enjoy a beautiful solo performance from her.

snippet.textDisplay:
This season"s top ten for me:
10) Ghoom Tana
9) Mujh se pehli si 
8) Baanware
7) Dekh Tera Kya
6)Sab Maya Hai 
5) Faasle
4) Us Rah Pr
3) Ranjish Hi Sahi
2)Naina Moray
1)Allah U Akbar
Just my personal opinion !!!!!!!
Man of the season: Jaffer Ziadi ( This man kept the true essence of Coke Studio alive with his mind blowing compositions and that faasle song which he sang...simply awesome) 
Biggest Disappointment : Sahir Ali Bagga ( i had very high expectations from him and he just didnt deliver...baazi was good but believe me, he can do much much better)
